and they're all
being reissued now.

00:20:06.020 --> 00:20:09.220 align:middle line:84%
And so I'm just mentioning
this, not to pick myself up

00:20:09.220 --> 00:20:10.870 align:middle line:90%
in any way--

00:20:10.870 --> 00:20:13.360 align:middle line:84%
I just feel I'm a
servant of these topics--

00:20:13.360 --> 00:20:15.477 align:middle line:84%
but to show the interest
is unprecedented.

00:20:15.477 --> 00:20:17.560 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Interest is now
really starting to rise.

00:20:17.560 --> 00:20:18.430 align:middle line:90%
That's fabulous.

00:20:18.430 --> 00:20:19.540 align:middle line:90%
That's good news.

00:20:19.540 --> 00:20:21.748 align:middle line:90%
I find that very uplifting.

00:20:21.748 --> 00:20:23.290 align:middle line:84%
OK, let's get into
a couple of things

00:20:23.290 --> 00:20:24.610 align:middle line:84%
because I want to
get into some dreams,

00:20:24.610 --> 00:20:26.650 align:middle line:84%
and what certain dreams
mean, and all that.

