But let's talk about some of
the more biological effects

00:20:31.000 --> 00:20:34.150 align:middle line:84%
like what REM does for
the being, for the body

00:20:34.150 --> 00:20:36.430 align:middle line:84%
and also what happens
when you're binging

00:20:36.430 --> 00:20:40.420 align:middle line:84%
on television on a screen with
blue light till late at night

00:20:40.420 --> 00:20:42.800 align:middle line:84%
because a lot of people
started that during COVID too.

00:20:42.800 --> 00:20:43.600 align:middle line:90%
>>CHEUNG: Yes.

00:20:43.600 --> 00:20:45.070 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:20:45.070 --> 00:20:48.190 align:middle line:84%
Netflix, et cetera, they
got a boom, didn't it?

00:20:48.190 --> 00:20:50.320 align:middle line:90%
We were all watching major--

00:20:50.320 --> 00:20:51.610 align:middle line:90%
binging on Netflix.

00:20:51.610 --> 00:20:54.010 align:middle line:84%
Your dreaming mind
will seize on things

00:20:54.010 --> 00:20:57.670 align:middle line:84%
in the day that have intense
emotional content to repackage

00:20:57.670 --> 00:20:58.663 align:middle line:90%
them for you at night.

00:20:58.663 --> 00:21:00.580 align:middle line:84%
However, you've got to
think of all the things

00:21:00.580 --> 00:21:02.350 align:middle line:84%
that you watched on television
and all the things that

00:21:02.350 --> 00:21:03.280 align:middle line:90%
happened in your day.

00:21:03.280 --> 00:21:07.060 align:middle line:84%
Why does your dreaming mind
hone in on one particular thing?

00:21:07.060 --> 00:21:10.420 align:middle line:84%
There are millions of
things it could choose.

00:21:10.420 --> 00:21:12.130 align:middle line:84%
So of course, what we
watch on television

00:21:12.130 --> 00:21:14.620 align:middle line:84%
is going to impact
our dream life.

00:21:14.620 --> 00:21:17.410 align:middle line:84%
However, you've got to realize
that you your dreaming mind,

00:21:17.410 --> 00:21:19.660 align:middle line:84%
which is very clever,
could choose anything.

00:21:19.660 --> 00:21:22.010 align:middle line:90%
It chooses that for a reason.

00:21:22.010 --> 00:21:27.310 align:middle line:84%
And I actually encourage
watching fantasy and--

00:21:27.310 --> 00:21:30.460 align:middle line:84%
but not two hours before you go
to sleep because that can have

00:21:30.460 --> 00:21:33.580 align:middle line:84%
