00:21:33.580 --> 00:21:35.950 align:middle line:84%
immersing yourself in
an alternative reality,

00:21:35.950 --> 00:21:38.890 align:middle line:84%
and that's what happens in
dreaming because I've also

00:21:38.890 --> 00:21:40.840 align:middle line:84%
found that there is
a strong connection

00:21:40.840 --> 00:21:43.060 align:middle line:84%
between vivid
dreaming and gamers.

