hack within Hollywood now,

00:22:33.190 --> 00:22:36.720 align:middle line:84%
dreamwork, to help
you embrace shadow

00:22:36.720 --> 00:22:39.220 align:middle line:84%
aspects of your character which
you're maybe not expressing.

00:22:39.220 --> 00:22:40.020 align:middle line:90%
Fascinating.

